reviewText: Most of these movies are worthy of a viewing, Some are excellent, and many of them are funny. A great deal for the price.
I love animals, so of course, I love all these movies.  Each has a good plot and are very entertaining.
arrived safely and was a gift - thanks so much and sorry for the late confirmation and appreciation - merry Christmas

The first movies on both dvd's are great for the family. It is a two-dvd set.  Got them at a local WALMART at low cost.  Once I can get the other 6 movies to play, then I will be alright.  Even if they don't, two great movies at that price is unbeatable.
